data.description: Completely move in ready single level townhome located on a quiet cul-de-sac off Quinlan Creek. Home features neutral and fresh paint throughout and on kitchen Cabinetry too, solid surface ceramic tile floors, and a wide open floor plan. Generous size kitchen with ample storage, solid surface counters, and all appliances convey. Off Kitchen, you have a laundry with with Washer and dryer, a nice size dining room, wet bar, and open to the living room with floor to ceiling fireplace. Abundance of Natural Light with sliding glass doors off kitchen (to front courtyard), Living Room, and Master Suite with access to the back patio. Split Bedroom floorplan, both with large walk in closets. So much Storage throughout! On the back patio you have an upper and lower deck, with a beautiful setting with trees overlooking the seasonal creek and bridge! You can also enjoy the wildlife that walks by.  Don't miss this one!
